stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> WAIT_FOR_SOF : Idle / Reset
    WAIT_FOR_SOF --> READ_FRAME_ID : On SOF (0xAA)
    READ_FRAME_ID --> READ_LENGTH : After 2 bytes
    READ_LENGTH --> READ_PAYLOAD : When length valid
    READ_LENGTH --> WAIT_FOR_SOF : When length invalid
    READ_PAYLOAD --> READ_CRC : After LENGTH bytes
    READ_CRC --> VERIFY_EOF : After 2 bytes
    VERIFY_EOF --> VALID_FRAME : On EOF (0x55) & CRC OK
    VERIFY_EOF --> WAIT_FOR_SOF : On CRC fail or invalid EOF
    VALID_FRAME --> WAIT_FOR_SOF : Frame handled
